          "id": "N030_TEMPLATE_READ",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The template is written in a tone that assumes someone will later ask why it existed. (pause)\n\nThe checkbox reads: \u201cI acknowledge receipt of required training materials.\u201d (pause)\n\nNot \u201cI completed.\u201d Not \u201cI understood.\u201d (pause)\n\nJust receipt\u2014training as a package delivered to a body.",
