          "text": "You reach for the \u201cright numbers\u201d and come up short. (pause)\n\nEither you lack access or your procedure isn\u2019t clean enough to risk it. (pause)\n\nThe machine keeps bland default contrast\u2014perfect for receipts, terrible for liability.",
