        {
          "id": "N121_PULL_NARR",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The pages are warm at the edges (pause) as if heat counts as authentication. (pause) The signature is real. (pause) The language around it is a fence.",
